<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="iddc708168-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee" identifier="/us/usc/t2/s22"><num value="22">§ 22.</num><heading> Oath of President of Senate</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">When a President of the Senate has not taken the oath of office, it shall be administered to him by any Member of the Senate.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="iddc708169-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee">(R.S. § 29.)</sourceCredit>
